proposal: Navigating the world of swaps, transactions, and token data can be like trying to find a needle in a haystack, but it looks like you've turned that haystack into a neatly organized toolbox with your APIs! Congrats on reaching 105 holders on the ETH network. If you're looking to expand your toolkit, our DEX and Lottery platforms could offer your community new ways to engage and share in your success. Let's make those APIs even more powerful together.
